&lt;h3&gt;Bonus&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are still some awaits that can be used in other iterations as &quot;map&quot;, &quot;filter&quot;, &quot;reduce&quot; but this is for another pill since some won&apos;t work and other can with some workarounds.&lt;/p&gt;
