&lt;p&gt;* Don&apos;t rely on these values as it is not a very reliable benchmark nor its results are too. But it shows a pattern...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;So, what do I use&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From the simpleness and according to my own (very simple) benchmark, I would use the Set method anytime I can.&lt;/p&gt;
